# AlphaSwarm Orchestrator Model
# Register with: ollama create alphaswarm-orchestrator -f modelfiles/Modelfile.orchestrator
#
# Base: qwen3.6:27b-nvfp4 (MLX format) — model decision 2026-06-11,
# benchmarked on this M1 Max 64GB (ollama 0.30.7):
#   qwen3.6:27b-q4_K_M (GGUF/llama.cpp): prefill  111 t/s, decode  9.0 t/s
#   qwen3.6:27b-nvfp4 (MLX, THIS):       prefill 3395 t/s, decode 11.3 t/s
# The advisory prompt is 5-8k tokens: MLX cuts its prefill from ~60s to ~2s
# and the full advisory call from ~4 min to ~2.5 min. Same 27B weights —
# still the strongest open model in the 64GB budget (beats Gemma 4 31B
# aggregate and Qwen3.5-397B on coding per Apr-2026 benchmarks).
#
# Requirements: OLLAMA_USE_MLX=1 (configure script persists it via
# LaunchAgent) and >=32GB unified memory; silent llama.cpp fallback
# otherwise. nvfp4 is text-only (no vision). num_ctx kept at 8192 to
# bound KV. Reasoning is default-on in qwen3.6; call sites pass
# think=False per 41.4-MODEL-DECISION-LOG.md.
FROM qwen3.6:27b-nvfp4
PARAMETER num_ctx 8192
PARAMETER temperature 0.7
PARAMETER num_gpu 999
